{"result": {"folders": ["lab1"], "nr": 1447, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2020-04-10T14:32:30Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"anon": "stud", "data": "k8uahqwwhmw6bm", "v": "all", "type": "create", "when": "2020-04-10T14:32:30Z", "uid_a": "a_0"}, {"anon": "full", "data": "k8uc7gda9nr44u", "to": "k8uahqwulz86bl", "type": "s_answer", "when": "2020-04-10T15:20:29Z", "uid_a": "a_1"}, {"anon": "full", "data": "k8ucbgyp6zr2h5", "type": "s_answer_update", "when": "2020-04-10T15:23:36Z", "uid_a": "a_1"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "stud", "uid_a": "a_0", "subject": "想请教一个关于中断号的问题", "created": "2020-04-10T14:32:30Z", "content": "<p>大家好&#xff0c;我想请教一个关于中断号的问题。</p>\n<p>在时钟初始化函数clock_init()最后&#xff0c;通过pic_enable(IRQ_TIMER)实现了对时钟中断的使能。</p>\n<p>pic_enable()里面的操作是&#xff0c;将相应比特的mask置零来得到的。这里IRQ_TIMER是0&#xff0c;也就是说是将irq_mask里面的第0位设置为0。</p>\n<p>我的疑惑是&#xff0c;在硬件方面&#xff0c;时钟产生一个中断&#xff0c;然后PIC通知CPU中断产生了。可是我并没有看到一个代码&#xff0c;将硬件与中断号联系在一起阿&#xff1f;中断的产生是通过level trigger 或者 egde trigger, 这两种触发方式pic只是知道时钟产生中断了&#xff0c;并不能知道时钟的中断号是多少呀&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>难道是每一个外设他的中断号都是固定好了的&#xff1f;时钟就是0&#xff0c;键盘就是1&#xff1f;那这样就不能灵活分配了呀&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>烦请老师或同学帮忙解答一下。</p>\n<p></p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["lab1", "student"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 98, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2020-04-10T15:20:29Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [{"role": "student", "name": "Guoqiang Zhong", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "k8mkxrs7jjp35j", "photo_url": null, "published": true, "us": false, "facebook_id": null}], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "k8uc7gd5d2u44t", "history": [{"anon": "full", "uid_a": "a_1", "subject": "", "created": "2020-04-10T15:23:36Z", "content": "<p>是的&#xff0c;据我所知&#xff0c;中断号的设置是由硬件完成的&#xff0c;而且是有固定标准的。因为有些中断必须要支持&#xff0c;所以在中断控制硬件里写死了一部分&#xff0c;这样比较快&#xff08;如果每次中断还要执行软件代码就有点慢了&#xff0c;即便可以给出硬件选项也会带来效率损耗&#xff0c;主要没必要&#xff09;。至于灵活分配&#xff0c;中断号还有些剩余&#xff0c;这部分可以留给更高层的设计者自己处理。</p>"}, {"anon": "full", "uid_a": "a_1", "subject": "", "created": "2020-04-10T15:20:29Z", "content": "<p>是的&#xff0c;据我所知&#xff0c;中断号的设置是由硬件完成的&#xff0c;而且是有固定标准的。因为有些中断必须要支持&#xff0c;所以在中断控制硬件里写死了一部分。至于灵活分配&#xff0c;中断号还有些剩余&#xff0c;这部分可以留给更高层的设计者自己处理。</p>"}], "type": "s_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": ["k8mkxrs7jjp35j"], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "k8uahqwulz86bl", "config": {"seen": {"554": 3, "1399": 4, "1310": 1, "714": 9, "835": 2, "945": 8, "1294": 7, "172": 6, "1183": 5, "340": 0}}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 3, "num_favorites": 0, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643170070563, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyv118v7nfl6dc"}